# Drivers directory
# Device drivers will be downloaded and stored here

Driver packages that can be installed:
- Android ADB & Fastboot Drivers
- Samsung USB Drivers
- Qualcomm QDLoader HS-USB Drivers
- MediaTek VCOM Drivers
- Apple Mobile Device Support
- Huawei HiSuite Drivers
- LG USB Drivers
- Motorola Device Manager

The application will manage driver downloads and installations automatically.
